    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Temporibus domini Leonis pape anno [quinto], die sexta
                        decima mensis februarii, indicione sexta, <placeName ref="#places/594"
                            >RAV(enne)</placeName>. Dum ade[sset quidem in] domum iuxta <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches">Sancti Stefani</orgName> domnus <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1596">Mainardus</persName>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1460"><placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposianus</placeName></orgName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>, <persName key="#Monks"><name ref="Wido">Uuido</name></persName> et 
                        <persName key="#Monks"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> <rs key="#Monks">monachi</rs>, 
                        <persName key="#Judge"><name ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName> <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs>, 
                        <persName><name ref="Morandus de Rainerio">Morandus
                            de Rainerio</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Hugo Cristianus">Ugo Cristianus</name></persName>,
                        <persName><name ref="Iohannes Faber">Iohannes faber</name></persName>, Belzetone et me presente
                        <persName key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Wido">Uuidone</name></persName> Dei misericordia tabell(ione) Rav(ennas), in nostrorum omnium
                        presencia adprehendens <persName><name ref="Albertus de Bricia">Albertus qui vocatur de Bricia</name></persName> virgam manu sua
                        misitque in manus prefati abbatis, dixit: 'Ecce spondeo et obligo me de illo
                        <rs key="#Landed_possessions">spacio terra</rs> in suburbio Rav(enne) posito quod a nobis per 
                        <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">enfiteosin</rs> habeo
                        quod neque ego neque mei filii vel nepotes aut successor illud alicui nemini
                        dabimus, si necesse est, nisi suprascripto monasterio aut donabimus neque in
                        custodiam vel commendacionem alicui dabimus quod sit ad damnacionem vel
                        contrarietatem aut dishonorem prefati monasterii vestri; et si facere
                        presumserimus, ipsa enfiteoseos cartula sit invalida'. Et postea paulolum
                        Iohannes faber similiter obligavit de alio spacio iuxta eum predictum quod
                        habebat ipse per enfiteoseos cartulam. Tunc prenominatus abbas ita accipiens
                        virgam, dixit: 'Deprecor vos omnes qui hic estis pro futuro testimonio'. Hoc
                        factum est sub die menseque et indicione suprascripta sexta, RAV(enne).</ab>
                </div>
